    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1889-02-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1889-02-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="218" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d218">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Preston</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New
                                        York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1889-02-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">February</hi> 16,
                                    1889</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Deputy collector of customs, after consultation with district attorney,
                            intends to clear this noon the <hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi>, now called
                            the <hi rend="italic">Conserva</hi>. In view of the proofs I am ready to
                            furnish, establishing that the <hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi> is Haytian
                            rebel property concealed under the flag of their Dominican allies, in
                            view of the further facts stated in my note of yesterday, and in view of
                            the state of war between the Republics of Hayti and Santo Domingo, I
                            must earnestly request that positive and immediate orders be given to
                            detain the <hi rend="italic">Madrid.</hi>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stephen Preston</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
